ontainer block-container mb-l mb-mobile-l"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 col-9 my-auto"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">A platform with purpose</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>We work to create a more equitable, inclusive and sustainable world for our band members, our creators and our listeners.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-9 col-offset-2 my-auto"><picture><source srcSet="/images/470x470/dei-landing-2-640.webp" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/470x470/dei-landing-2-640.jpg" media="(max-width: 767px)" type="image/jpeg"/><source srcSet="/images/470x470/dei-landing-2-940.webp" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/webp"/><source srcSet="/images/470x470/dei-landing-2-940.jpg" media="(min-width: 768px)" type="image/jpeg"/><img src="/images/470x470/dei-landing-2-940.jpg" alt="" style="max-width:470px;max-height:470px" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_image__nIttw textimage_imageLargeMobile__vDuBQ"/></picture></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-center col-18 col-offset-3"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-4 line-140 size-5-mobile"><p>Keep scrolling to learn more about our response to some of today’s most pressing challenges and the opportunities we’re seizing to drive change.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-3" class="layout-section py-section pt-xl pt-mobile-xl LayoutSection_folderSwitch__oIPgg"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Diversity, Equity and Inclusion</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-2"><p>Creating a more diverse, equitable and inclusive culture where everyone belongs.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="deib" style="top:calc(100% - )" class="layout-section py-section bg-lavender pt-50% pb-xxxl pb-mobile-xxxl LayoutSection_topImageBg__PEXrI LayoutSection_folder__aFC_Y"><div id="deib-animation-trigger" class="deiblp_absoluteContainer__lFc8r"><div class="deiblp_relativeContainer__WJ4Tr"><div id="hand_1" class="deiblp_hand_1__fQXAA"><img src="/esg-animation/DEIBLP/hand_1.svg" alt="hand_1"/></div><div id="hand_2" class="deiblp_hand_2__qvHTy"><img src="/esg-animation/DEIBLP/hand_2.svg" alt="hand_2"/></div><div id="hand_3" class="deiblp_hand_3__bCe6P"><img src="/esg-animation/DEIBLP/hand_3.svg" alt="hand_3"/></div><div id="hand_4" class="deiblp_hand_4__Tpyrz"><img src="/esg-animation/DEIBLP/hand_4.svg" alt="hand_4"/></div><div id="hand_5" class="deiblp_hand_5__ZuVmg"><img src="/esg-animation/DEIBLP/hand_5.svg" alt="hand_5"/></div><div class="deiblp_bottom__CDT9F"><img src="/esg-animation/DEIBLP/bottom.svg" alt="bottom"/></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-l mb-mobile-l"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-2"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">What it means to us</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>Creating a diverse, equitable and inclusive culture where anyone feels like they belong takes an inclusion mindset, awareness and intentionality. But perhaps most of all, it takes action. Here’s what Diversity, Equity, Inclusion & Belonging means to us.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU undefined container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel mb-xl mb-mobile-xl"><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_bigDrag__NWIDO"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="flipcard_flipCard__c_tWC"><div class="flipcard_flipCardInner__ErT45"><div class="flipcard_flipCardFront__0SzDG"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/diversity.svg&quot;)"></div><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Diversity</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">We build our band to be representative of the artists, consumers and creators on our platform.</p></button></div><div class="flipcard_flipCardBack__oGYxb"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM simplecard_backIcon__LFqBC"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Diversity</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">The range of unique characteristics, perspectives, similarities and differences an individual or organization has that shapes workplace and culture. These may include national origin, sexual orientation, race, disability and the list goes on.</p><span class="simplecard_spacer__pqERP is-hidden-desktop"></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_bigDrag__NWIDO"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="flipcard_flipCard__c_tWC"><div class="flipcard_flipCardInner__ErT45"><div class="flipcard_flipCardFront__0SzDG"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/equity.svg&quot;)"></div><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Equity</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">We work to ensure everyone has fair and equitable access to opportunities and advancement.</p></button></div><div class="flipcard_flipCardBack__oGYxb"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM simplecard_backIcon__LFqBC"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Equity</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">The fair and equitable treatment of all, so that everyone has access to the opportunities, systems and resources needed to do their best work.</p><span class="simplecard_spacer__pqERP is-hidden-desktop"></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_bigDrag__NWIDO"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="flipcard_flipCard__c_tWC"><div class="flipcard_flipCardInner__ErT45"><div class="flipcard_flipCardFront__0SzDG"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/inclusion.svg&quot;)"></div><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Inclusion</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">We lead with empathy and are always looking for ways to infuse inclusion into our culture.</p></button></div><div class="flipcard_flipCardBack__oGYxb"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM simplecard_backIcon__LFqBC"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Inclusion</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">The intentional action to connect each employee to our mission and values, to encourage collaboration, flexibility, and fairness; so that Spotifiers from all backgrounds thrive.</p><span class="simplecard_spacer__pqERP is-hidden-desktop"></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_bigDrag__NWIDO"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="flipcard_flipCard__c_tWC"><div class="flipcard_flipCardInner__ErT45"><div class="flipcard_flipCardFront__0SzDG"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_image__BFiih" style="background-image:url(&quot;/images/svg/belonging.svg&quot;)"></div><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Belonging</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">We don’t just want to foster a sense of belonging in our company culture — we want to amplify it across the world. </p></button></div><div class="flipcard_flipCardBack__oGYxb"><button class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside p-relative simplecard_container__JygsH simplecard_cursor__ie1ob clear-button simplecard_white__TQp_3 simplecard_shadow__kx_27 simplecard_hasLongText__roZS2"><div class="simplecard_iconContainer__FP1HU"><span class="simplecard_icon__2aybM simplecard_backIcon__LFqBC"></span></div><p class="ma-0 mt-xs fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white simplecard_title__0aOVN"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Belonging</p><p class="ma-0 mb-0 fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white simplecard_longText__ps8c8 mr-40">The experience of Spotifiers when they feel seen and heard for who they are, accepted and valued as members of the band.</p><span class="simplecard_spacer__pqERP is-hidden-desktop"></span></button></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Belong here</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Discover everything we’re doing to promote Diversity, Equity, Inclusion and Belonging at Spotify.</p></div><a href="/diversity-equity-impact/diversity-equity-inclusion-belonging" aria-label="Learn more" class="size-7 size-8-mobile fw-normal clear-button buttons_filled__uuK0X mt-xs">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-2" class="layout-section py-section bg-white pt-xl pt-mobile-xl LayoutSection_folderSwitch__oIPgg"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Challenging the stigma of mental health </h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-2"><p>We believe that everyone’s experiences of mental health – from illness to wellbeing – should be respected, welcomed and championed. Heart & Soul is how we’re making this happen.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="mental-health" style="top:calc(100% - )" class="layout-section py-section bg-light-orange pt-50% pb-xxxl pb-mobile-xxxl LayoutSection_topImageBg__PEXrI LayoutSection_folder__aFC_Y"><div id="mentalhealth-animation-trigger" class="mentalhealthanimationlp_absoluteContainer__acA4q"><div class="mentalhealthanimationlp_relativeContainer__KMw9N"><div id="leftCloud" class="mentalhealthanimationlp_leftCloud__6Vmd6"><img src="/esg-animation/MentalHealthLP/front-left-cloud.svg" alt="left-cloud"/></div