t="/images/120x120/piano-for-healing-240.jpg"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="rounded-20 bg-white pt-l pb-l pt-mobile-l pb-mobile-l pl-mobile-0 pr-mobile-0 mr-m ml-m mr-mobile-xs ml-mobile-xs p-relative mb-mobile-xl bigcontentblock_container__5AMaV mb-xl"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 textimage_swap__3qGht col-offset-1 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-9"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Heart &amp; Soul</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>In 2018, we launched Heart & Soul, our global mental health initiative. Heart & Soul focuses on three primary goals in mental health: raising awareness, providing support, and reducing stigma. Together, they bring focus and impact to all our initiatives.</p><p> By fostering a supportive environment where people look after themselves and each other, we can create a culture where everyone feels like they belong, and no one suffers in silence.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-9 col-offset-2 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/heart-and-soul.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Tune into you</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Explore our mental health initiatives and how we’re building a stigma-free workplace for our people.</p></div><a href="/diversity-equity-impact/mental-health" aria-label="Learn more" class="size-7 size-8-mobile fw-normal clear-button buttons_filled__uuK0X mt-xs">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-4" class="layout-section py-section pt-xl pt-mobile-xl LayoutSection_folderSwitch__oIPgg"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Supporting communities through social impact</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-2"><p>We’re choosing to step up for society, act with purpose and use our platform for good. We want to help shape a world that is welcoming to all.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="social-impact" style="top:calc(100% - )" class="layout-section py-section bg-dark-green pt-50% pb-xxxl pb-mobile-xxxl LayoutSection_topImageBg__PEXrI LayoutSection_folder__aFC_Y"><div id="socialimpact-animation-trigger" class="socialimpact_absoluteContainer__YWGaa"><div class="socialimpact_relativeContainer__iZo_A"><div id="building" class="socialimpact_building__5Ah75"><img src="/esg-animation/SocialImpact/Middleground.svg" alt="building"/></div><div id="rightHill" class="socialimpact_rightHill__HLWZJ"><img src="/esg-animation/SocialImpact/Background.svg" alt="right-hill"/></div><div id="leftHill" class="socialimpact_leftHill__qdUut"><img src="/esg-animation/SocialImpact/Foreground.svg" alt="left-hill"/></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-ml mb-mobile-ml"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Play your part</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>From current affairs to social equity, be part of the important conversations happening on our platform right now.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockC