rapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Elevating underrepresented creators</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez mb-0">We’re committed to removing the barriers that make it harder for creators from marginalized groups to flourish.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Paying it forward</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez mb-0">Giving guides all aspects of how we show up in the world. Our external philanthropy work aligns with our internal work on climate action, civic engagement, mental health, employee wellbeing, and gender and racial equity.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Inspiring users to be part of the democratic process</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez mb-0">We bring messages about civic engagement to our audience wherever they are – and from the voices they trust the most. Our campaigns are nonpartisan and focus on making voting easier and more exciting for our audience.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop"></span></div></div></div></div><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1 carousel_smallWide__hslvE"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div class="rounded-20 rounded-15-mobile hover-inside defaultcard_container__boBhR defaultcard_white__9B5wJ defaultcard_smallWide__qdoFa defaultcard_shadow__3PFwc defaultcard_hasLongText__ILAOs"><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2"></span><p class="ma-0 mt-s fw-normal size-4 line-120 color-white defaultcard_title__QsVbh"><span class="sr-only">Title:</span>Responsible storytelling</p><p class="ma-0 mb-s fw-light size-6 size-8-mobile line-150 color-white defaultcard_longText__t7Hez mb-0">For Spotify, media responsibility means supercharging the impact of our audio platform through accurate, trustworthy and progressive storytelling. We prioritize stories from historically marginalized communities and focus on issues that resonate with our listeners.</p><span class="defaultcard_spacer__e0Dn2 is-hidden-desktop"></span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Shaping the world together</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>Read about our Social Impact initiatives and how we’re helping to shape a more equitable world.</p></div><a href="/diversity-equity-impact/social-impact" aria-label="Learn more" class="size-7 size-8-mobile fw-normal clear-button buttons_filled__uuK0X mt-xs">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></section><section id="section-5" class="layout-section py-section pt-xl pt-mobile-xl LayoutSection_folderSwitch__oIPgg"><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Let’s be part of the solution</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-2"><p>The climate crisis is one of the most pressing issues of our time. We must all work to be part of the solution so that people and the planet can thrive.</p></div></div></div></section><section id="climate-action" style="top:calc(100% - )" class="layout-section py-section bg-dark-blue pt-50% pb-xl pb-mobile-xl LayoutSection_topImageBg__PEXrI LayoutSection_folder__aFC_Y LayoutSection_lastFolder__c8K_3"><div id="climate-action-animation-trigger" class="climateaction_absoluteContainer__EWoOu climateaction_overlaped__ATqms"><div><div id="star" class="climateaction_star__eWyJi"><img src="/esg-animation/ClimateAction/star.svg" alt="star"/></div><div id="flyingStar" class="climateaction_flyingStar__CVyXS"><img src="/esg-animation/ClimateAction/flying-star.svg" alt="flying-star"/></div></div><div id="earth" class="climateaction_relativeContainer__XKsGz" style="border-radius:100rem 100rem 0 0"><div id="leftContinent" class="climateaction_leftContinent__jC5zE"><img src="/esg-animation/ClimateAction/left-continent.svg" alt="left-continent"/></div><div id="rightContinent" class="climateaction_rightContinent__XtpJS"><img src="/esg-animation/ClimateAction/right-continent.svg" alt="right-continent"/></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-xl mb-mobile-xl"><div class="row"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><h2 class="size-2 line-100 bg-color-active">Changing the tune</h2></div></div><div class="row mt-xxs mt-mobile-xxs"><div class="col-16 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 text-mt-0 size-4 line-140 size-6-mobile line-150-mobile bg-color-active col-offset-4 text-center text-center-mobile"><p>There’s no clear blueprint for an audio streaming business like ours to reach net zero emissions by the end of 2030. But that doesn’t mean we’re not taking action – far from it.</p></div></div></div><div class="container block-container mb-xxl mb-mobile-xxl"><div class="row"><div class="col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-offset-2 textimage_mobileSwap__DU83h col-12"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>We believe it’s our responsibility to drive progress in this space, and to share our journey with our partners and peers. Our immediate focus is to measure and understand our climate impact along our value chain so that we can prioritize the right actions, scale them and then collaborate to reduce it.</p><p>Of course, we’re already making changes – increasing energy efficiency in our offices, supporting internal climate communities and updating our climate tracking and risk assessment processes.</p></div></div></div><div class="mt-mobile-s col-offset-1 col-8 col-14-mobile col-offset-mobile-5 my-auto"><img src="/images/svg/icon-megaphone-light.svg" alt="" class="image-fluid rounded-20 textimage_svg__KIp_G"/></div></div></div><div class="container block-container"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-6 text-center"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-120">Follow our progress</h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-6 line-150 size-7-mobile"><p>See everything we’re doing to lessen our impact on the planet on our Climate Action page.</p></div><a href="/diversity-equity-impact/climate-action" aria-label="Learn more" class="size-7 size-8-mobile fw-normal clear-button buttons_filled__uuK0X mt-xs">Learn more</a></div></div></div></div></section><section class="layout-section py-section pb-xl pb-mobile-xl LayoutSection_afterFolder__ZBz_K"><div class="container block-container mb-l mb-mobile-l"><div class="row"><div class="col-12 col-24-mobile col-offset-mobile-0 col-12 col-offset-2"><div class="mb-m mb-mobile-m mb-0-last"><h3 class="mb-xxxs mb-mobile-xxs bg-color-active size-3 line-110">Amplifying historically marginalized voices and moments on our platform </h3><div class="text-mt-0 link-light-bg bg-color-active size-5 line-150 size-6-mobile"><p>Throughout the year, we celebrate various moments that center underrepresented communities and the issues they care about. We use creative storytelling to celebrate these groups and to drive community impact. We strive to tell untold tales of expression and progress from these communities that spark a greater understanding and inspire action.</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="carousel_blockContainer__X1hfU undefined container block-container fluid mb-0 mb-mobile-0"><div class="drag-carousel"><div class="swiper-container carousel_swiper__jqMlV" modules="[object Object]"><div class="swiper-wrapper"><div class="swiper-slide carousel_swiperSlide___umLf carousel_drag__7kIL1"><div class="carousel_fadeIn__XeC5Q"><div style="width:inherit;height:inherit"><div class="bg-white bottomimage